headline: Gear Up for United (UAL) Q4 Earnings: Wall Street Estimates for Key Metrics
summary: Looking beyond Wall Street's top-and-bottom-line estimate forecasts for United (UAL), delve into some of its key metrics to gain a deeper insight into the company's potential performance for the quarter ended December 2025.

headline: United Customers Can Now Order Fresh, United Economy Meals Before Their Flight
summary: United customers can now order fresh, United Economy meals like burgers and sandwiches before their flight through the airline's website and mobile app. This change prioritizes giving customers more choice and ensuring they get the meals they want, while also helping the airline's catering operation run more efficiently and supporting efforts to reduce food waste.

headline: Airlines to save big money on fuel as new weight-loss pills gain popularity, Wall Street says
summary: Jefferies argued that a 10% reduction in average passenger weight could translate into roughly 2% total aircraft weight savings.
